---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Gabriele Pellegrini
---

<div class="container">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <p>Breve descrizione su di te e il tuo lavoro. Una presentazione professionale che descriva chi sei e cosa fai.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="tags-section">
    <h2>Tags</h2>
    <div class="tags-list">
      {% for tag, posts in collections | dichotomize %}
        {% if tag != "all" and tag != "posts" %}
          <a href="/tags/{{ tag }}/" class="tag">
            {{ tag }} <sup>{{ posts.length }}</sup>
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

<section>
    <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
  <ul class="journal-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
    <a href="{{ post.url }}">
      <li>
        <span>{{ post.data.title }}</span>
        <hr>
        <small>{{ post.date | formatDate }}</small>
        {% if post.data.description %}
          <div class="post-desc">{{ post.data.description }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
      <p class="more-link"><a href="/journal/">View all posts â†’</a></p>
</section>









</div>